title: TDP-8 | Social Proof | Reward 50 $RETOKEN for HeroX.com sign-up | Project TokenTown
body:
# Overview
I propose that we reward 50 $RETOKEN to community members that sign-up for our HeroX.com team for tokentown (25 for each track: hardware/software)

> * 24h Snapshot proposal period for voting
> * *This will allow us to execute confidently and operate democratically / transparently within the DAO framework we are creating.*

# Join HeroX Project Teams: TokenTown by REtoken DAO 
> *Request to Join our HeroX teams*
* [TokenTown by REtoken DAO (Hardware track)](https://www.herox.com/solarprizeR5hardware/team/14294)
* [TokenTown by REtoken DAO (Software track)](https://www.herox.com/solarprizeR5software/team/14295)

# Related Proposals / Additional Details
* [Discord "temp check" post"](https://discord.com/channels/877883581903564860/882418077004877834/892982834195742741)
* [GitHub Page: PROJECT: "TokenTown" | American-Made Solar Prize Round 5](https://github.com/REtokenDAO/projects/edit/main/2021/HeroX/sr5/)
* [RIP-3 | PROJECT: "TokenTown" | American-Made Solar Prize Round 5](https://snapshot.org/#/retokendao.eth/proposal/QmYZxcsaqY4yFBzMHTAppsu8mmtfjbnuJWtS1AzhK1r3g2)

# Vote
* Yes | This is a great project!!
* No | not a fan of this one
